ary.jpg|80px]] |- | [[Adam Weishaupt]] || 1748–1830 || German || Founded the [[Illuminati|Order of the Illuminati]]. || [[File:Johann Adam Weishaupt.jpg|80px]] |- | [[Christoph Martin Wieland]] || 1733–1813 || German || Philosopher and poet. || [[File:Weimar Anna Amalia Bibliothek@C.M. Wieland.JPG|80px]] |- | [[Christian Wolff (philosopher)|Christian Wolff]] || 1679–1754 || German || Philosopher and mathematician. || [[File:Johann Georg Wille - Portrait of Christian Wolff - WGA25767.jpg|80px]] |- | [[Mary Wollstonecraft]] || 1759–1797 || English|| Writer, and pioneer feminist. || [[File:Mary Wollstonecraft by John Opie (c. 1797).jpg|80px]] |}
